02:02:36,582 --> 02:02:37,682
(blade pierces flesh)

1695
02:02:46,792 --> 02:02:48,760
♪

1696
02:02:56,469 --> 02:02:58,436
♪

1697
02:03:05,711 --> 02:03:07,679
♪

1698
02:03:15,855 --> 02:03:17,822
♪

1699
02:03:25,498 --> 02:03:27,465
♪

