02:04:01,133 --> 02:04:04,102
(chanting continues)

1703
02:04:15,080 --> 02:04:17,248
(chanting continues)

1704
02:04:23,923 --> 02:04:26,858
(rock scraping)

1705
02:04:31,030 --> 02:04:33,198
(scraping stops)

1706
02:04:37,069 --> 02:04:39,204
