1711
02:05:10,269 --> 02:05:13,438
Now I can't ask him to forgive me.

1712
02:05:27,453 --> 02:05:29,420
♪

1713
02:05:38,364 --> 02:05:39,664
(gasps)

1714
02:05:43,569 --> 02:05:46,604
♪

1715
